Class CollectBackReferencesVisitor

Visitor
public class CollectBackReferencesVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor

Helper that collect all segments a node is part of, all ways a node or segment is part of and all areas a node is part of. Deleted objects are not collected.
